From: "Ryan X. Charles" <ryan@ryanxcharles.com>
Date: Tue, 3 Mar 2026 07:44:58 -0600
Subject: [PATCH 53/53] Add bidirectional socket IPC
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit

The XPC wires grew tangled and old,
Each tab a new connection to hold.
One socket now streams
Both directions — it seems
Much simpler than endpoints of gold.

Co-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.6 <noreply@anthropic.com>
